1. Activate the mod_communication Module from Zotonic Admin and restart zotonic to start the gen_server.

2. Add the Twilio Number and URL to the site config file 
   {twilioNumber, "0123456789"},
   {twilioURL, "http://www.xxxxxx.com/"},

2. To create conference call do the following.
  PhoneList = ["3522192940", "3522469644"],

  if you want default invite message then call
  z_communication:create_call(PhoneList, [], Context).
  
  if you want custom invite message then call
  z_communication:create_call(PhoneList, Message, Context).

3. To send sms to List of Phone Numbers.
   PhoneList = ["3522192940", "3522469644"],

   z_communication:send_sms(PhoneList, Message, Context).

4. To send Email to List of Email Ids.
   EmailList = ["sanketgawade7@gmail.com", "jeff@5nineshq.com"],

   z_communication:send_email(EmailList, Template, Vars, Context).
   
